{"tid":1425773,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"總商會歸邊：香港總商會強烈譴責近期香港發生的一連串暴力行為。","createTime":"2019-08-06T20:37:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T00:23:39.000Z","uid":189150,"like":3,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e113af53eae7dde5d6347a782ba4a20be9fa8f4f","tid":1425773,"uid":189150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T20:37:00.000Z","msg":"香港總商會今日（6日）聲明，強烈譴責近期香港發生的一連串暴力行為。聲明指過去數星期暴力行為不斷升級，小撮人士的街頭暴力與大部分和平示威者追求的目標完全相違背，這不但有損本港國際金融中心的聲譽，以及中小企業的運營，更甚者是影響一般普羅大眾安全及生計。<br />\n<br />\n 總商會希望香港社會能盡快回復和平與繁榮，唯此只可以透過法治才能達成。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n英文statement：<br />\n<br />\n HKGCC Strongly Condemns Violence<br />\n<br />\nFor Immediate Release<br />\n<br />\nWe strongly condemn the escalating violence which has affected Hong Kong over the last few weeks. It has not only affected Hong Kong&rsquo;s reputation as an international financial center, but also the small and medium size enterprises and most importantly undermined the safety and livelihood of ordinary Hong Kong people.<br />\n<br />\nThe violent minority is completely destroying the aspirations of the majority peaceful demonstrators.<br />\n<br />\nWe all hope and wish that Hong Kong returns to peace and prosperity but this can only happen if we return to the rule of law."},{"pid":"f47be12b6c46e36cf7d5da3ea6dd07f007f73f03","tid":1425773,"uid":189150,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T20:48:32.000Z","msg":"睇黎 中共開始迫人歸邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75380f0396ac2fde4fa66ff8401726b7fd046505","tid":1425773,"uid":180124,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T20:51:25.000Z","msg":"收皮啦之前元朗單野又叫政府回應訴求"},{"pid":"0a0f8a694b98c2b9bc9bf1ae47fa66f3018f8c60","tid":1425773,"uid":76216,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T20:53:47.000Z","msg":"傻仔黎<br />\n以為發展到現在咁可以變返以前咩<br />\n冇嫁啦 一係革命成功 一人一票選舉<br />\n一係就會好似新疆咁 等經濟收皮"},{"pid":"cd70504a39670687b4bbc8c8c0979865b4feec2b","tid":1425773,"uid":189150,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"75380f0396ac2fde4fa66ff8401726b7fd046505","tid":1425773,"uid":180124,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T20:51:25.000Z","msg":"收皮啦之前元朗單野又叫政府回應訴求"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T20:54:48.000Z","msg":"所以覺得已經中共記者會後收到order了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd0997005e44b0c44cfb374bcea8ed3cf09594d1","tid":1425773,"uid":117418,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T20:57:39.000Z","msg":"認真諗吓不消費運動<br />\n其實個個星期六日有活動大家都已經少咗消費<br />\n平日不如多啲留喺屋企食飯<br />\n我呢幾個星期真係冇出過街食飯<br />\n晚晚自已煮, 湯水都飲多咗<br />\n冇人消費睇吓班友仲點撐政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43e7f310c0c08149b213175e269ab9e6b9d145c8","tid":1425773,"uid":180124,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"cd70504a39670687b4bbc8c8c0979865b4feec2b","tid":1425773,"uid":189150,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"75380f0396ac2fde4fa66ff8401726b7fd046505","tid":1425773,"uid":180124,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T20:51:25.000Z","msg":"收皮啦之前元朗單野又叫政府回應訴求"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T20:54:48.000Z","msg":"所以覺得已經中共記者會後收到order了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T20:57:53.000Z","msg":"香港人要做多樣野罷買係真<br />\n琴日都覺難<br />\n依家覺得要去收商家佬皮"},{"pid":"181229068c247bff6de7470149801cb1a5976c61","tid":1425773,"uid":189150,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"43e7f310c0c08149b213175e269ab9e6b9d145c8","tid":1425773,"uid":180124,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"cd70504a39670687b4bbc8c8c0979865b4feec2b","tid":1425773,"uid":189150,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"75380f0396ac2fde4fa66ff8401726b7fd046505","tid":1425773,"uid":180124,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T20:51:25.000Z","msg":"收皮啦之前元朗單野又叫政府回應訴求"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T20:54:48.000Z","msg":"所以覺得已經中共記者會後收到order了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T20:57:53.000Z","msg":"香港人要做多樣野罷買係真<br />\n琴日都覺難<br />\n依家覺得要去收商家佬皮"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T21:09:26.000Z","msg":"罷買我覺得要做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但成效可能唔大，我當你全港四成藍絲三成和理非三成支持衝擊<br />\n當全部支持衝擊＋一半和理非都撐罷買，都係得四成半人會做<br />\n唔出街食飯唔買衫褲鞋都要買gear，後生仔示威都要出街醫肚<br />\n咁搞最多咪零售低十幾廿個％，壓力唔夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n中共大把手段搞掂你地  例如應承之後放多d自由行落黎<br />\n班商家佬都係會撐中共"},{"pid":"50dc510a690dd675c2c6b87e7eb14ff769841c62","tid":1425773,"uid":55913,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T21:16:15.000Z","msg":"就算聽日開始完全無事<br />\n所有人都唔開心唔消費<br />\n最重要係支那係匯率操縱國<br />\n一定爆到7彩"},{"pid":"cac4805f769a4cedc5d5b31137074f4c8ae7a2c1","tid":1425773,"uid":39733,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T21:22:54.000Z","msg":"我又覺得呢個回應正常喎，未必係黨壓落嚟<br />\n之前打咁多日，影響商界嘅係黑社會同黑警<br />\n今次係罷工同阻塞交通，係抗爭者影響營商<br />\n商會要咁出聲都係合理（雖則好短視）<br />\n記住佢哋係商會，講政治都係以營商角度為主"},{"pid":"4a8cf3c3051854e4b35debb0c3da5c4628f43996","tid":1425773,"uid":230511,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T21:52:05.000Z","msg":"去到呢個地步有冇可能大家都當冇事發生過第二個回歸平靜？<span style=\"color: red;\">冇可能</span><br />\n<br />\n拉左幾百個手足香港同佢地有關係有接觸既人有幾多？有冇可能大家當冇佢地存在過？<span style=\"color: red;\">冇可能</span><br />\n<br />\n黑警做咁多陰質野變晒過街老鼠，有冇可能可以再正正常常走去茶餐廳蛇王吹水？<span style=\"color: red;\">冇可能</span><br />\n<br />\n年輕一代撻著左既革命心有冇可能冚得熄？<span style=\"color: red;\">冇可能</span><br />\n<br />\n因為呢度仲未係中國，呢度係香港<br />\n呢場運動咁走落去結果必然會係兩個極端<br />\n香港人贏返香港，將舊制推倒重建，或者係呢個世界再冇香港呢個地方，以後只有支港"},{"pid":"5bdf6b8bb9b274be2ecfa2cee46fff8ca7b1bec8","tid":1425773,"uid":235754,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"181229068c247bff6de747014